title: Nepos Napos
synopsis: You see a whale-shaped cloud drifting in the blue sky. What you don't see is a strange land of Nepos Napos that lies above it. Don't you want to know what is happening and how everybody lives up there?
voices: ['Sendai, Eri', 'Katou, Emiri', 'Kakihara, Tetsuya', 'Izumi, Kumiko', 'Tanaka, Yuuko', 'Sakamoto, Chika']
